deviations_disco_ball_desc: Extends the duration of other Whims.
deviations_frog_the_leaper_desc: Greatly enhances jump height but also consumes stamina.
deviations_electric_eel_desc: Increases the power limit of Generators according to Electric Eel Energy level.
deviations_harveseed_desc: When life is fading away, new vitality is unleashed.
deviations_dreamcatcher_desc: When in danger, spits a spider web to restrain your enemies.
deviations_space_turner_desc: After use, creates a Teleport Door and summons teammates to you.
deviations_fetch-a-lot_bunny_desc: Automatically gathers shrubs when activated. The higher the Deviant Energy level, the more efficient the gathering is.
deviations_ice_bottle_desc: Produces a magical adhesive ice block.
deviations_buzzy_bee_desc: Increases the mutation chance of planted crops. The higher the Deviant Energy level, the higher the mutation chance is.
deviations_chefosaurus_rex_desc: Increases your cooking proficiency. The higher the Deviant Energy level, the greater the proficiency increase.
deviations_h37_desc: Loots chests in different areas. The higher the Deviant Energy level, the better the goodies it will bring back.
deviations_gingerbread_house_desc: Changes into any object in the scene after use.
deviations_hug-in-a-bowl_desc: Restores Sanity to full upon consumption.
deviations_atomic_lighter_desc: Randomly deals varying instances of damage. Grants extra loot upon killing monsters.
deviations_nutcracker_desc: Patrols your Territory and attacks suspicious intruders. The higher the Deviant Energy level, the more effective its attack.
deviations_logging_beaver_desc: Goes out logging when activated. The higher the Deviant Energy level, the more efficient the logging is. Will use a Logging Operation Platform first if available.
deviations_the_digby_boy_desc: Goes out mining when activated. The higher the Deviant Energy level, the more efficient the mining is. Will use a Mining Operation Platform first if available.
deviations_rebecca_desc: Summon Mitsuko to the territory to play piano and improve the Deviants' energy recovery efficiency.
deviations_masonic_pyramid_desc:
The first hit after going out of combat and into a dive must be a Crit.
Alerts you when an enemy outside your field of view aims at you.
deviations_snow_globe_desc: Inflicts Slowdown on targets upon hit and Frozen upon multiple hits.
deviations_growshroom_desc: Automatically plants seeds and accelerates crop growth. The higher the Deviant Energy rating, the faster the growth.
deviations_rain_man_desc: Boosts the vitality of crops. The higher the Deviant Energy rating, the greater the vitality. It also provides the right amount of irrigation water.
deviations_strange_door_desc: Once built, it allows teleportation between two doors.
deviations_atomic_snail_desc: Allows you to sprint a short distance in the air after use.
deviations_night_watch_lamp_desc: Patrols the territory and attacks suspicious targets. Splits to conjure laser guns every once in a while.
deviations_hydronaut_fish_desc: Gathers Purified Water outside the territory. Operating the Water Filter or Brewing Barrel increases conversion efficiency.
deviations_party_monkey_desc: Constructing this facility will draw the aggro of monsters within its vicinity.
deviations_upper_world_spawn_desc: Gain immunity from some damage but you cannot take any actions.
deviations_flame_essence_desc: Increases the production efficiency of the Furnace and Electric Furnace.
deviations_extradimensional_cat_desc: Accompanies its owner to sleep to make sure that they're fully energetic the next day.
deviations_orb_lightning_desc: Increases the performance of nearby Turrets upon use.
deviations_paper_doll_desc: When the Stardust Resonant Filter, walls, or floors take damage, they will automatically recover Durability. The higher the Deviant Energy level, the quicker the Durability recovery. Also enjoy a chance of finding unexpected rewards when you kill Deviants that have invaded your Territory.
deviations_lethal_rabbit_desc: Goes out exploring and hunting with a chance to obtain animal resources. The higher the Deviant Energy level, the better the goodies it will bring back.
deviations_artisan's_touch_desc: Repairs the least durable gear you equip. The item disappears after use and only applies to the gear that you crafted.
deviations_tar_pudding_desc: Gathers fuel around the territory. While working at the fuel refining facility, accelerates fuel conversion efficiency.
fishes_koi_fish_(cloud)_desc: Renowned for its beautiful colors and elegant swimming, the koi fish is also believed to bring good luck and prosperity.
fishes_barracuda_(aquamarine)_desc: The barracuda fish is a rare delicacy, prized for its tender, succulent meat.
fishes_black_bass_(pure_white)_desc: The meat from the largemouth black bass is pretty darn good — practically bone-free. It's a smart pick for your everyday fish feast.
fishes_guppy_(peacock)_desc: The Guppy fish is one of the most beloved aquarium species, adored for its colorful tailfins
fishes_sardine_(blood_mark)_desc: Instead of refering to a specific species, "sardine" used to be a collective term for various small fish that werecommonly canned.
fishes_bighead_carp_(gold_knife)_desc: The bighead carp is a large and robust species, fun to look at and easy to care for.
fishes_angelfish_(purple_dawn)_desc: Angelfish is a popular choice for home aquariums, admired for its elegant appearance and peaceful demeanor.
fishes_tilapia_(red_giant)_desc: The tilapia is easy to care for and enjoyable to watch, making it a perfect choice for your aquarium.
fishes_northern_pike_(blood_jade)_desc: Northern pike meat is tasty, but it's got a ton of fiddly bones. It's not one for those who like their food fast and easy.
fishes_sunfish_(black_rose)_desc: The Sunfish is a delightful sight in your home aquarium for its vibrant array of colors and spirited behavior.
fishes_rainbow_trout_(blue_porcelain)_de: The coloring and patterns of the fish vary widely depending on habitat and spawning condition. The rainbow trout is distinguished by the reddish band along either side that resembles a rainbow.
fishes_sucker_fish_(spotted)_desc: Despite its unappealing name, the sucker fish is actually packed with flavor and nutrients.
fishes_oscar_fish_(amber)_desc: Known for its beautififul patterns and intelligence, the Oscar fish is entertaining and enjoyable to own.
fishes_pompano_(opal)_desc: This silvery fish with a forked tail is a favorite among seafood lovers for its delicious and flavorful taste.
fishes_tilapia_desc: Tilapia is tender, tasty, and doesn't have too many bones. An excellent source of protein and amino acids.
fishes_bighead_carp_desc: Bighead Carp thrive in fertile water environments. A gentle, slow-moving fish, it was often farmed, back in the old days.
fishes_sucker_fish_desc: Despite its unappealing name, the sucker fish is actually packed with flavor and nutrients.
fishes_pompano_desc: Pompano are easy to catch using light tackle. Tasty and succulent.
fishes_barracuda_desc: Barracuda in different waters have very different behaviors, but they all have "solitary" in common, and adult Barracuda have few natural predators.
fishes_oscar_fish_desc: The Oscar Fish has two large black spots on its tailfin that look like eyes. This makes it difficult for the Oscar Fish's prey to figure out which end is its head.
fishes_angelfish_desc: The Queen Angelfish, with its graceful bearing, is hailed as the "Queen of Tropical Fish." Its lifespan can exceed 10 years in captivity.
fishes_koi_carp_desc: The koi fish is considered a symbol of good fortune in many Eastern cultures.
fishes_electric_eel_desc: Works in the Territory to provide power to Generators.
fishes_sunfish_desc: The Sunfish is so named because of its rounded body shape.
fishes_large_blue_cichlid_desc: A large, glossy Cichlid species. Reminds you of a sparkling gem.
fishes_red_cichlid_desc: Cichlid with vibrant red coloring, can be a striking addition to any aquarium.
fishes_jade-eye_cichlid_desc: The calming sapphire color of blue cichlids is sure to fix any blue feelings
fishes_large_yellow_cichlid_desc: A large, golden Cichlid species. Would make a striking addition to an aquarium.
fishes_white_cichlid_desc: The snowy color of the white cichlid always brings a sense of tranquility
fishes_guppy_desc: The Guppy fish is one of the most beloved aquarium species, adored for its colorful tailfins
fishes_sea_bass_desc: The sea bass is a rare delicacy, prized for its tender, succulent meat.
fishes_golden_cichlid_desc: The glittering gold color of yellow cichlids makes them a symbol of fortune.
fishes_lionhead_cichlid_desc: A colorful Cichlid species. It's like an underwater work of art.
fishes_arowana_desc: Arowana, also known as Dragon Fish, is a majestic species and highly admired by aquarists.
fishes_carp_desc: Carp is a common fish. Bony, but tasty, plentiful, and cheap.
fishes_mackerel_desc: The mackerel is an impatient fish and will quickly spoil unless frozen straight out of the water. In the days before fishing boats came with reliable cold storage, mackerel were often discarded or used as cat food.
fishes_rainbow_trout_desc: The rainbow trout doesn't care what colors you think should be in a rainbow. The rainbow trout doesn't conform to your outdated chromatic ideals. In fact, the rainbow trout doesn't even know what a rainbow is. Checkmate.
fishes_salmon_desc: Salmon, known for their migratory habits, have become a reliable food source.
fishes_sardine_desc: Back in the day, "sardine" wasn't so much a kind of fish as a catch-all term for any small piscatorial critter that could be caught near the surface and canned.
fishes_longnose_gar_desc: The longnose gar is a crucial apex predator in the ecosystem, playing a vital role in preventing the overpopulation of certain species.
fishes_largemouth_black_bass_desc: The meat from the largemouth black bass is pretty darn good — practically bone-free. It's a smart pick for your everyday fish feast.
fishes_northern_pike_desc: Northern pike meat is tasty, but it's got a ton of fiddly bones. It's not one for those who like their food fast and easy.
